    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meat-free mince</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
