    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mince is cooking, chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Halve the<strong> lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Combine the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lime</strong> with the <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> lime yoghurt</strong></p>",
