    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince is browned, reduce the heat to medium-high and add the<strong> smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add the <strong>honey</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the mince becomes crispy and sticky – this is your<strong> sticky chilli meat-free mince</strong></p>",
