    {
      "instruction": "<p>Build your own burritos by layering up a <strong>warmed tortilla </strong>with some<strong> brown rice</strong>, a spoonful of <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and a dollop of the <strong>sticky chilli meat-free mince</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over some<strong> grated cheese</strong> and a drizzle of<strong> lime yoghurt</strong>, then roll your <strong>burritos</strong> up tightly</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
